        <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-black uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">THE MORTGAGE BROKER WEBSITE PROBLEM</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">Most mortgage broker websites fail to generate applications. Outdated design from 2015, NMLS number buried in footer, no current rates, no loan calculator, difficult application process, not mobile-optimized, no lender relationships visible, missing compliance badges. Homebuyer = biggest purchase of life = cautious = needs trust = needs to verify you're legitimate licensed professional. Amateur website = questionable = risky = skip = call broker with professional site. Mortgage = trust business = website credibility = applications.</p>
      </div>

