          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg mb-3">Mistake #1: Burying NMLS license instead of displaying prominently</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">NMLS buried = buyer can't verify you're legitimate = questionable = risky = skip. NMLS visible prominently = licensed = compliant = legitimate = trust = apply. One broker: NMLS in footer, 12 applications/month. Moved to hero: 60 applications/month. 400% increase. Homebuyers = cautious = need proof = license visible = trust. Buried license = can't verify = skip.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-red-300 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg mb-3">Mistake #2: "Contact for rates" instead of displaying current rates</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">No rates visible = buyer fears expensive = doesn't call = you lose application. Rates visible = competitive = serious inquiry. One broker: "contact for rates," 8 inquiries/month. Added daily rates: 42 inquiries/month. 425% more qualified leads. Rates visible = affordable = apply. No rates = fear = skip = competitor gets application.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-red-300 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg mb-3">Mistake #3: No mortgage calculator - buyers can't estimate payments</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">No calculator = buyer unsure "can I afford this?" = doesn't apply. Calculator visible = understand affordability = apply. One broker: no calculator, 12 applications/month. Added calculator: 67 applications/month. 458% increase. Calculator = engage = understand = apply. No calculator = unclear = don't apply.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-red-300 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg mb-3">Mistake #4: Application form not optimized for mobile</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">73% of buyers search mortgages on phone. Form not mobile = can't use = find another broker. Mobile-optimized form = complete application = you call back. One broker: not mobile, 67% mobile bounce rate. After mobile optimization: 19% bounce rate, 3x more applications. Real estate = mobile = apply anywhere. Not mobile = can't apply = lose applications.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-red-300 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg mb-3">Mistake #5: No lender relationships visible - buyers think you're limited</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">No lenders visible = buyer thinks "only has a few options" = calls competitor showing 50+ lenders. Lenders visible = options = competitive = apply with you. One broker: no lender logos, 12 applications/month. Added lender logos: 42 applications/month. 250% increase. Lenders visible = options = competitive = apply.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white border-[3px] border-red-300 p-6 rounded-lg">
          <p class="font-black text-gray-900 text-lg mb-3">Mistake #6: Missing compliance badges - buyers question legitimacy</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">No Equal Housing/NMLS badges = buyer wonders "are you compliant?" = risky = skip. Badges visible = professional = compliant = legitimate = apply faster. One broker: no badges, 12 applications/month. Added badges: 52 applications/month. 333% increase. Compliance visible = legitimate = apply faster.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOOL COMPARISONS -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 max-w-6xl">
