            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-1">CMS for Rate Updates</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-gray-700">Build rate update CMS: update daily rates once, displays across site automatically. David: "Today's Rates" updated daily, buyers know rates current, apply.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="border-l-[3px] border-red-500 pl-4 py-2 bg-red-50/50 rounded-r">
            <p class="font-black text-gray-900 mb-1">Learning Curve</p>
